        Registers an event listener for the given component and adds a recorder for this component.
        Parameters:
        component - the component which the recorder should be registered for.
        _recorder - The recorder, which should be added for the given component.
        Returns:
        true if the given component is a composite and DEAL can continue to get subcomponents of the given component during traversing, false otherwise.
